WEBVTT

00:08.421 --> 00:11.161
If the household keeps spending
without income,

00:11.461 --> 00:13.871
no matter how wealthy we are,
we'll run out of money.

00:14.011 --> 00:16.640
That's why my mother asked
my grandfather

00:16.641 --> 00:19.040
to get His Lordship a position
at the North Warden's Office

00:19.041 --> 00:21.000
as the Deputy Commander.

00:21.001 --> 00:22.141
(Appointment Letter)

00:24.401 --> 00:25.941
This is the appointment letter.

00:27.721 --> 00:29.240
I wanted to share this piece of news

00:29.241 --> 00:31.581
together with the Duke and you.

00:36.721 --> 00:38.271
That's more like it.

00:38.441 --> 00:39.840
Remember this well.

00:39.841 --> 00:41.020
As a wife,

00:41.021 --> 00:42.720
the greatest virtue

00:42.721 --> 00:45.381
is to help your husband succeed
in his career.

00:45.601 --> 00:46.741
Do you understand?

00:48.821 --> 00:51.280
His Lordship was supposed
to collect this appointment letter

00:51.281 --> 00:52.930
at the Ministry of Personnel in person.

00:52.931 --> 00:54.461
But my grandfather already got it.

00:55.081 --> 00:57.960
His Lordship only needs to meet
the one from the Ministry

00:57.961 --> 00:59.301
to take up the post.

01:00.321 --> 01:01.461
All right.

01:01.641 --> 01:02.920
You must never forget

01:02.921 --> 01:05.901
to remind him about this appointment.

01:07.401 --> 01:08.541
I won't.

01:12.961 --> 01:14.000
My Lord,

01:14.001 --> 01:15.520
the sky is about to clear up.

01:15.521 --> 01:17.701
Why are you packing up
the paintings in a rush?

01:18.881 --> 01:21.480
I've made plans with Youming
to do landscape painting in Jiaozhou.

01:21.481 --> 01:22.560
What?

01:22.561 --> 01:23.800
Are you planning a long trip?

01:23.801 --> 01:24.451
You can't go.

01:24.461 --> 01:26.531
Grandfather has arranged a meeting
with the Ministry of Personnel.

01:26.541 --> 01:28.581
You must meet with them.

01:29.241 --> 01:30.541
Let's discuss the meeting

01:30.601 --> 01:31.901
when I get back.

01:32.921 --> 01:34.061
I'm leaving now.

01:35.721 --> 01:36.861
My Lord,

01:36.921 --> 01:38.720
aren't you going to ask
what it is about?

01:38.721 --> 01:40.240
Grandfather secured a position for you.

01:40.241 --> 01:41.840
It's a position at the Warden's Office.

01:41.841 --> 01:43.740
He'll be leaving for Liaodong
in a few days.

01:43.741 --> 01:45.090
We must meet

01:45.091 --> 01:46.440
to finalize the details.

01:46.441 --> 01:47.581
Ming,

01:50.481 --> 01:52.421
I've already made plans
to go landscape painting.

01:52.681 --> 01:55.021
If I don't go,
I'll be breaking my promise.

01:55.721 --> 01:56.941
Just wait until I return.

01:57.921 --> 01:59.981
My Lord.

02:00.121 --> 02:01.040
Sister-in-law hopes

02:01.041 --> 02:02.720
you can rise in your career.

02:02.721 --> 02:05.381
If you don't take up this position,
she'll start complaining again.

02:05.411 --> 02:06.701
Just let her complain.

02:07.081 --> 02:09.301
It's not worth being a corrupt official
who seeks power.

02:11.401 --> 02:12.271
My Lord!

02:12.281 --> 02:15.141
My mother begged my grandfather
for several days to secure this position.

02:15.161 --> 02:16.101
Ming,

02:16.561 --> 02:18.141
don't you know me?

02:18.281 --> 02:20.381
I've never cared
for titles or official positions.

02:22.001 --> 02:22.920
Are you forcing me

02:22.921 --> 02:24.381
to become someone I despise?

02:30.281 --> 02:31.461
My Lord!

03:59.121 --> 04:03.320
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

04:03.321 --> 04:06.480
=Episode 21=

04:06.481 --> 04:09.221
(Yizhi Hall)

04:26.541 --> 04:28.751
You've been reviewing these ledgers
for several days.

04:29.211 --> 04:30.300
You should get some rest.

04:30.301 --> 04:31.441
Let me help you do it.

04:33.141 --> 04:34.281
Are you sure?

04:41.461 --> 04:42.601
Inventory?

04:42.751 --> 04:44.331
This is the inventory for my ledgers.

04:44.531 --> 04:46.541
My ledgers are over there.

04:47.241 --> 04:48.741
(Ledgers)

04:51.281 --> 04:52.661
You have so many businesses?

04:55.361 --> 04:58.021
How did you manage to keep it hidden?

05:00.121 --> 05:03.301
Do you know Mr. Zhaoning
from the Capital?

05:04.041 --> 05:05.040
Of course.

05:05.041 --> 05:07.760
Mr. Zhaoning's businesses
are all over the Capital.

05:07.761 --> 05:08.901
Everyone knows that.

05:09.961 --> 05:12.360
Mr. Zhaoning has a name,

05:12.361 --> 05:14.400
properties, and a family lineage.

05:14.401 --> 05:17.501
But this person doesn't exist.

05:17.641 --> 05:19.021
How did you know?

05:23.561 --> 05:25.621
Don't tell me you're...

05:29.401 --> 05:30.781
I have too many businesses

05:30.801 --> 05:32.301
and no one to trust.

05:32.521 --> 05:34.741
To avoid drawing attention,

05:35.561 --> 05:36.960
I registered all my businesses

05:36.961 --> 05:39.181
under Mr. Zhaoning's name.

05:39.321 --> 05:41.520
So no matter how people investigate,

05:41.521 --> 05:43.141
they can't trace it back to me.

05:45.841 --> 05:47.501
When Wang Yingxue married my father,

05:47.961 --> 05:49.341
my mother passed away.

05:49.401 --> 05:51.571
My grandmother wanted
to give me something to rely on,

05:51.581 --> 05:53.240
so she asked both the Dou Family
and the Wang Family

05:53.241 --> 05:54.741
to give me three thousand taels each.

05:54.801 --> 05:56.840
Later, I moved to the manor
in the countryside

05:56.841 --> 05:58.461
to live with my grandmother.

05:58.561 --> 06:02.021
But I couldn't spend the money
without making some.

06:02.201 --> 06:03.280
So I invested the money

06:03.281 --> 06:05.021
in the Futing's sea trade.

06:05.281 --> 06:08.101
Thanks to the Ding Army
for eliminating the pirates.

06:08.361 --> 06:09.440
Since then,

06:09.441 --> 06:11.240
my business has flourished,

06:11.241 --> 06:12.701
growing bigger and bigger.

06:16.521 --> 06:17.661
What's the matter?

06:18.561 --> 06:20.301
The happier you talk about it,

06:21.241 --> 06:22.581
the sadder I feel

06:23.001 --> 06:25.181
about not meeting you earlier.

06:27.561 --> 06:29.861
Since you were young,
you grew up enduring hardships

06:30.041 --> 06:32.461
with no one to rely on.

06:32.881 --> 06:34.261
When we first met,

06:35.321 --> 06:36.621
I even bullied you.

06:37.221 --> 06:38.461
I should be punished for that.

06:42.001 --> 06:43.141
I'll hold you to that later.

06:43.241 --> 06:44.640
I'll note it down in the ledger.

06:44.641 --> 06:45.901
I'll do it now.

06:46.601 --> 06:47.741
Yes, do it now.

06:57.721 --> 07:00.341
You don't have to write
with your right hand anymore.

07:01.501 --> 07:03.021
You can switch back to your left hand.

07:04.761 --> 07:06.101
In Yizhi Hall,

07:06.481 --> 07:07.821
feel free to do as you please.

07:11.761 --> 07:13.301
You're so good to me.

07:13.401 --> 07:15.621
I don't even know how to repay you.

07:16.561 --> 07:18.101
How about

07:18.641 --> 07:20.461
I give you half my wealth?

07:21.441 --> 07:22.701
That's not right.

07:22.901 --> 07:24.941
Your father has only just started
to approve of me.

07:25.321 --> 07:27.360
If I take half your wealth,

07:27.361 --> 07:28.981
won't he turn against me?

07:35.081 --> 07:37.761
I'll go to the kitchen and make you
a bowl of calming herbal soup.

07:38.681 --> 07:39.821
Come back soon.

08:22.321 --> 08:25.470
♪I want to hide like the moon♪

08:25.471 --> 08:28.911
♪Like a butterfly drawn to flowers♪

08:29.201 --> 08:35.350
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart
that turns to longing♪

08:35.351 --> 08:39.090
♪Like the sun waiting
for the flying wild geese♪

08:39.091 --> 08:42.461
♪The sound of weapons chasing
the long whip♪

08:42.961 --> 08:49.021
♪Never tired after a hundred battles,
because of you♪

09:04.921 --> 09:06.501
- Good morning, sir.
- Good morning.

09:07.641 --> 09:08.781
Don't go inside.

09:09.281 --> 09:10.581
Ms. Longevity

09:16.081 --> 09:17.000
was up all night.

09:17.001 --> 09:19.080
Let her sleep a little longer.

09:19.081 --> 09:20.501
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

09:21.161 --> 09:22.010
Let's go.

09:22.011 --> 09:22.880
One more thing.

09:22.881 --> 09:25.080
Instruct the kitchen
to prepare chicken soup

09:25.081 --> 09:26.360
and pigeon soup

09:26.361 --> 09:28.581
for her to regain her strength.

09:30.481 --> 09:32.021
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

09:33.881 --> 09:35.221
Did they...

09:35.461 --> 09:37.641
- Do you have any other instructions?
- Do you have any other instructions?

09:38.641 --> 09:40.120
The bed was also dirty last night.

09:40.121 --> 09:41.381
When Ms. Longevity wakes up,

09:41.481 --> 09:43.160
tidy up and change the bedding.

09:43.161 --> 09:44.661
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

09:47.161 --> 09:49.461
- Little Lord...
- We're having Little Lord soon.

09:49.611 --> 09:51.251
It could be a Little Young Lady.

10:01.121 --> 10:01.970
Madam,

10:01.971 --> 10:03.680
we're done changing the bedding.

10:03.681 --> 10:05.221
We'll take our leave, then.

10:05.521 --> 10:06.661
All right.

10:14.311 --> 10:15.160
Why

10:15.161 --> 10:16.821
did you wake me up so late?

10:16.881 --> 10:18.800
His Lordship ordered us not
to disturb you.

10:18.801 --> 10:21.421
He wanted you to sleep in.

10:21.441 --> 10:22.621
How improper.

10:23.041 --> 10:25.501
I have a pile of ledgers to review.

10:25.921 --> 10:28.341
Plus, we're staying at Yizhi Hall.

10:28.401 --> 10:29.741
If this gets out,

10:30.081 --> 10:31.860
there will surely be gossip again.

10:31.861 --> 10:34.031
Everything is fine
between you and His Lordship.

10:34.231 --> 10:36.291
You don't need to worry
about such things anymore.

10:39.801 --> 10:41.280
She's intelligent,

10:41.281 --> 10:42.901
and they are so perfectly matched.

10:43.241 --> 10:45.280
She brought so many dowries.

10:45.281 --> 10:47.741
No one in the Capital can match that.

10:47.801 --> 10:50.621
No wonder His Lordship holds
Her Ladyship in such high regard.

10:51.921 --> 10:52.840
I heard

10:52.841 --> 10:55.400
His Lordship and Her Ladyship
were up until dawn.

10:55.401 --> 10:58.741
The lights in their room
didn't go out until almost dawn.

11:09.361 --> 11:11.061
Madam, the soup is ready.

11:11.081 --> 11:12.221
Soup?

11:13.561 --> 11:15.261
Chicken soup.

11:17.001 --> 11:18.901
Pigeon soup.

11:20.001 --> 11:21.981
Did he tell you to prepare these too?

11:22.041 --> 11:25.821
He even had the bed linens
cleaned separately.

11:26.201 --> 11:27.461
Why?

11:27.561 --> 11:29.800
The servants are all saying

11:29.801 --> 11:31.920
that you and His Lordship
are very affectionate.

11:31.921 --> 11:34.680
They estimate there might be a baby
on the way soon.

11:34.681 --> 11:36.080
What nonsense.

11:36.081 --> 11:38.240
It's because I was too tired

11:38.241 --> 11:40.141
from reviewing ledgers last night.

11:40.521 --> 11:42.021
As for the bed linens,

11:42.601 --> 11:44.541
I don't know why he did that.

11:46.601 --> 11:48.581
Song Yantang is ruining my reputation!

11:48.641 --> 11:49.680
Young Lady,

11:49.681 --> 11:51.880
you're his wife now.

11:51.881 --> 11:53.560
How is this ruining your reputation?

11:53.561 --> 11:54.640
But we...

11:54.641 --> 11:56.200
We were reviewing the ledgers,

11:56.201 --> 11:57.840
nothing else.

11:57.841 --> 11:58.680
I understand.

11:58.681 --> 12:01.640
Next time, when you
and His Lordship review ledgers,

12:01.641 --> 12:03.240
we'll make sure not to disturb you.

12:03.241 --> 12:05.360
Reviewing ledgers means
reviewing ledgers.

12:05.361 --> 12:07.400
It doesn't imply anything else.

12:07.401 --> 12:08.520
Madam,

12:08.521 --> 12:11.541
the more you try to explain,
the worse it sounds.

12:11.721 --> 12:12.560
I understand it now.

12:12.561 --> 12:14.600
So reviewing ledgers

12:14.601 --> 12:15.880
is just a cover

12:15.881 --> 12:17.440
for a pleasant company.

12:17.441 --> 12:18.720
What are you talking about?

12:18.721 --> 12:20.760
You're getting more and more shameless,

12:20.761 --> 12:23.021
- aren't you?
- Oh, please forgive me.

12:25.721 --> 12:27.741
What are you all chatting about
so happily?

12:30.081 --> 12:31.221
Have a seat.

12:33.481 --> 12:34.621
Su Lan,

12:35.361 --> 12:36.581
serve the soup to His Lordship.

12:37.361 --> 12:38.501
Yes, Madam.

12:49.521 --> 12:50.661
Another bowl.

12:57.921 --> 12:59.061
Another one.

13:25.001 --> 13:27.341
- My dear...
- You're busy with official duties.

13:27.441 --> 13:29.861
This morning, you instructed
the servants to prepare the soup

13:29.921 --> 13:32.261
and took the time to worry
about the bedding.

13:32.801 --> 13:34.781
With such thoughtfulness,

13:34.801 --> 13:36.421
you should have more of the soup.

13:36.481 --> 13:37.621
Have another bowl.

13:38.561 --> 13:39.861
It's all right.

13:40.081 --> 13:41.301
Just have some more.

13:41.921 --> 13:43.000
Fill it up.

13:43.001 --> 13:44.141
Yes, Madam.

13:47.921 --> 13:49.061
Here you go.

13:51.041 --> 13:53.221
I'll tell the kitchen not
to make too much next time.

14:00.841 --> 14:02.440
His Lordship didn't report for duty?

14:02.441 --> 14:03.960
I heard he's gone on a trip.

14:03.961 --> 14:06.141
She even helped him pack.

14:09.841 --> 14:11.341
Bring Dou Ming here.

14:11.481 --> 14:12.621
Yes, Your Grace.

14:17.721 --> 14:18.861
Sister-in-law.

14:19.641 --> 14:22.181
So tell me what happened.

14:24.361 --> 14:25.821
His Lordship has a stubborn temper.

14:26.281 --> 14:28.920
I hope you can persuade him.

14:28.921 --> 14:30.720
You can't even handle your own husband!

14:30.721 --> 14:32.661
What kind of mistress are you?

14:32.961 --> 14:34.600
You don't have any money.

14:34.601 --> 14:36.381
You can't even support your husband.

14:36.561 --> 14:37.560
Tell me.

14:37.561 --> 14:39.440
What's the point of the Wei Family

14:39.441 --> 14:40.821
to have a daughter-in-law like you?

14:41.441 --> 14:43.200
The family's prosperity depends

14:43.201 --> 14:44.981
on the lady of the house.

14:45.681 --> 14:46.981
Look at Dou Zhao!

14:47.561 --> 14:49.151
Boxes and boxes of gold and silver

14:49.161 --> 14:51.071
are being moved
to the Duke of Ying's Residence.

14:51.081 --> 14:52.581
And look at you!

14:53.041 --> 14:55.541
Do you resemble the lady of the house?

14:57.241 --> 14:58.461
Well, it's not surprising.

14:58.721 --> 15:01.101
The apple doesn't fall far
from the tree.

15:02.361 --> 15:03.640
You're just like your mother!

15:03.641 --> 15:04.781
Sister-in-law,

15:04.801 --> 15:05.920
you can criticize me.

15:05.921 --> 15:08.061
But don't insult my mother!

15:08.281 --> 15:10.461
She dared to do those disgraceful things

15:10.961 --> 15:13.261
but couldn't bear
to let others talk about it?

15:14.841 --> 15:16.741
You must have learned
the habit of talking back

15:17.081 --> 15:19.061
from your mother, right?

15:20.041 --> 15:21.781
From now on,

15:22.281 --> 15:24.621
you should follow me

15:24.681 --> 15:26.381
and learn some rules.

15:28.241 --> 15:29.821
His Lordship is not at home.

15:30.041 --> 15:31.501
Learning the rules can wait

15:31.721 --> 15:33.240
until His Lordship returns.

15:33.241 --> 15:34.381
Why?

15:34.521 --> 15:36.901
As the Duchess of Jing,

15:36.961 --> 15:39.120
I can't teach you?

15:39.121 --> 15:41.880
Madam, say it directly
if you're not happy with something.

15:41.881 --> 15:43.461
Why do you have to humiliate...

15:43.841 --> 15:45.321
How dare you interrupt?

15:45.331 --> 15:46.731
What right do you have to hit her?

15:46.741 --> 15:48.541
I'm hitting the servant!

15:49.561 --> 15:52.341
Since you are a daughter-in-law
of the Wei Family,

15:53.681 --> 15:56.701
you must follow the Wei Family's rules.

16:01.321 --> 16:02.461
Madam,

16:03.521 --> 16:04.661
are you all right?

16:06.241 --> 16:07.840
With your care,

16:07.841 --> 16:09.181
I'm fine.

16:09.281 --> 16:12.861
But Madam, you have to do the morning
and evening greetings every day.

16:13.521 --> 16:16.141
You're going to have a hard time.

16:16.521 --> 16:18.360
Let Wenxiang accompany me

16:18.361 --> 16:20.381
to the greetings every day.

16:21.161 --> 16:22.741
So as not to anger Sister-in-law.

16:22.751 --> 16:25.161
What kind of sense is it
for a married daughter of the family

16:25.171 --> 16:26.741
to return and impose her own rules?

16:26.761 --> 16:28.640
The Duchess of Jing

16:28.641 --> 16:30.720
is clearly unhappy with her own life.

16:30.721 --> 16:32.021
So she's tormenting you

16:32.081 --> 16:33.861
as the Duke is away.

16:34.841 --> 16:35.981
It's all right.

16:36.921 --> 16:38.181
I can take it.

16:50.001 --> 16:52.821
The sound of that abacus has been
clattering on for over ten days now.

16:53.441 --> 16:56.101
I can hear that annoying sounds
even in my dreams.

16:57.561 --> 16:59.501
When will it ever end?

17:00.321 --> 17:01.461
What is it again?

17:01.681 --> 17:04.301
(Lofty Morality)

17:05.041 --> 17:06.341
Why are you here?

17:06.441 --> 17:08.741
I heard Yantang's wife is expecting.

17:09.601 --> 17:11.400
What nonsense is this?

17:11.401 --> 17:12.871
They've only been married a few days.

17:12.881 --> 17:15.501
The imperial physician from the palace
already checked her pulse,

17:15.521 --> 17:17.551
and said she was expecting twins,
a boy and a girl.

17:17.561 --> 17:18.621
That's right.

17:18.871 --> 17:19.720
Who said that?

17:19.721 --> 17:21.520
It came from the wet nurse

17:21.521 --> 17:23.560
of Imperial Physician Li's

17:23.561 --> 17:26.501
third son's second aunt.

17:30.001 --> 17:31.141
Lyu Zheng!

17:31.641 --> 17:32.781
Someone!

17:33.281 --> 17:35.221
Bring Butler Lyu here!

17:35.521 --> 17:36.880
Yes, Your Grace.

17:36.881 --> 17:38.621
The entire neighborhood...

17:38.841 --> 17:39.840
I mean

17:39.841 --> 17:41.701
half of the capital is saying

17:42.241 --> 17:45.661
His Lordship and his wife
are very affectionate.

17:45.721 --> 17:47.680
Every day, he instructed the kitchen

17:47.681 --> 17:49.821
to prepare soup to nourish her.

17:49.961 --> 17:51.101
They're saying...

17:54.561 --> 17:55.741
What did they say?

17:56.121 --> 18:00.221
They're saying the Duke's household
will soon have a baby.

18:01.521 --> 18:02.640
You fool!

18:02.641 --> 18:03.941
Calm down, Your Grace.

18:03.961 --> 18:05.680
I asked you to investigate
about the money.

18:05.681 --> 18:08.101
Yet, you bring me these baseless rumors!

18:08.481 --> 18:10.480
It's not entirely baseless.

18:10.481 --> 18:11.680
Think about it.

18:11.681 --> 18:14.701
If Her Ladyship gives birth to a son,

18:14.881 --> 18:18.000
wouldn't Second Young Master
have even less hope?

18:18.001 --> 18:19.421
Get out of my sight.

18:19.761 --> 18:20.840
I said, get lost!

18:20.841 --> 18:22.261
Get lost!

18:24.001 --> 18:25.141
Come back here!

18:30.961 --> 18:33.421
That matchmaker was certain

18:33.541 --> 18:35.960
that Dou Zhao was nothing more
than a boorish country woman,

18:35.961 --> 18:37.421
headstrong and unruly.

18:37.641 --> 18:38.781
But now it's clear

18:38.961 --> 18:41.421
there's something suspicious
about her background.

18:41.921 --> 18:44.421
Go and dig deeper.

18:44.601 --> 18:47.461
Find out exactly who she really is.

18:49.121 --> 18:50.261
Yes, Your Grace.

18:53.641 --> 18:55.120
(Tea)

18:55.121 --> 18:56.840
Dou Zhao is the richest person
in Zhending.

18:56.841 --> 18:58.240
She has countless businesses

18:58.241 --> 18:59.560
and is extremely wealthy.

18:59.561 --> 19:00.600
That's right.

19:00.601 --> 19:01.741
Wait.

19:01.801 --> 19:04.591
Didn't you say she lost all her money

19:04.601 --> 19:06.960
and handed over her businesses
to her stepmother to manage?

19:06.961 --> 19:08.360
You heard wrong.

19:08.361 --> 19:11.541
The businesses handed to her stepmother
are the ones losing money.

19:11.561 --> 19:13.981
On Fourth Young Lady Dou's wedding day,

19:14.041 --> 19:16.800
the dowry procession stretched
for miles.

19:16.801 --> 19:17.960
It was grander

19:17.961 --> 19:21.360
than the weddings of many noble families

19:21.361 --> 19:23.800
in the Capital.

19:23.801 --> 19:26.160
Fourth Young Lady Dou is known
for her kindness.

19:26.161 --> 19:29.440
Everyone in Zhending knows her.

19:29.441 --> 19:31.520
That year, Zhending had heavy rains.

19:31.521 --> 19:33.600
If Fourth Young Lady Dou

19:33.601 --> 19:36.301
hadn't waived some of the rent
at her manor,

19:36.401 --> 19:38.480
many families would have been forced

19:38.481 --> 19:39.760
to sell their children.

19:39.761 --> 19:42.480
But you said she was a shrew.

19:42.481 --> 19:44.501
You called her an ingrate.

19:44.921 --> 19:46.600
You misheard us.

19:46.601 --> 19:48.920
Madam Wang is the shrew and the ingrate.

19:48.921 --> 19:50.280
Fourth Young Lady Dou

19:50.281 --> 19:52.560
was raised well
and is known for her filial piety.

19:52.561 --> 19:54.581
Everyone in the area knows that.

19:54.601 --> 19:56.141
Young Master Pang disguised himself

19:56.201 --> 19:57.901
as a bandit

19:58.241 --> 20:00.240
to force her into marriage.

20:00.241 --> 20:02.461
It was like a toad dreaming
of dining on caviar!

20:02.481 --> 20:04.440
Wasn't it Fourth Young Lady Dou

20:04.441 --> 20:07.301
who forced herself
to marry Young Master Pang?

20:07.481 --> 20:09.181
You got it wrong.

20:09.321 --> 20:10.160
Not at all.

20:10.161 --> 20:12.560
Fourth Young Lady Dou is upright

20:12.561 --> 20:14.040
and generous.

20:14.041 --> 20:15.200
Everyone in the area

20:15.201 --> 20:17.560
- has benefited from her kindness.
- That's right.

20:17.561 --> 20:21.501
Young Master Pang even dared to file
a complaint at the county office.

20:21.641 --> 20:24.600
But in the end, he got punished himself.

20:24.601 --> 20:26.021
There's no mistake in that.

20:27.921 --> 20:29.061
I get it now!

20:29.401 --> 20:32.141
You all conspired to deceive me!

20:32.721 --> 20:33.861
No...

20:38.961 --> 20:40.661
Who is this disgusting thing asking

20:40.681 --> 20:43.421
about Fourth Young Lady Dou?

20:44.481 --> 20:46.781
We're from the Duke of Ying's Residence.

20:47.121 --> 20:48.581
Who are you?

20:48.801 --> 20:50.621
How dare you kidnap me?

20:50.841 --> 20:53.501
How dare you impersonate members
of the Duke of Ying's household?

20:53.961 --> 20:55.101
Slap him.

20:57.681 --> 20:59.160
Mercy, Old Madam!

20:59.161 --> 21:01.080
I was just trying to make a living

21:01.081 --> 21:02.800
and only following orders.

21:02.801 --> 21:04.541
Then I'll ask you one more time.

21:04.881 --> 21:07.061
Are you
from the Duke of Ying's Residence?

21:07.761 --> 21:08.680
Yes, I am.

21:08.681 --> 21:10.880
We're from the Duke of Ying's Residence.

21:10.881 --> 21:12.021
Slap him!

21:16.561 --> 21:17.701
Never mind.

21:18.521 --> 21:19.941
Stubborn fool.

21:22.121 --> 21:23.280
Drown him in the pond?

21:23.281 --> 21:24.421
Yes, Old Madam.

21:24.601 --> 21:26.301
No, don't!

21:27.601 --> 21:30.261
I'm not
from the Duke of Ying's Residence.

21:30.601 --> 21:33.901
The Duke of Ying's household and I
are sworn enemies!

21:34.881 --> 21:36.381
Now, that's more like it.

21:36.601 --> 21:37.741
Let him go.

21:39.121 --> 21:40.621
You didn't reveal

21:40.801 --> 21:42.821
that I sent you there, did you?

21:43.241 --> 21:44.421
Your Grace,

21:44.601 --> 21:47.421
I would rather die

21:47.841 --> 21:52.061
than divulge even a word
about the Duke of Ying's Residence.

21:52.201 --> 21:54.680
I only said I was a matchmaker
from far away,

21:54.681 --> 21:56.821
here to propose a marriage.

21:57.281 --> 21:59.981
So, is Dou Zhao truly
the richest person in Zhending?

22:00.201 --> 22:03.000
The entire area around Zhending
has benefited from her generosity?

22:03.001 --> 22:04.440
Yes.

22:04.441 --> 22:06.000
Fourth Young Lady Dou

22:06.001 --> 22:07.800
is not some country girl.

22:07.801 --> 22:10.261
They're all in cahoots.

22:10.361 --> 22:12.981
I risked my life

22:13.081 --> 22:16.061
to bring this news to you,
Your Grace.

22:20.531 --> 22:22.141
I fell for it!

22:22.771 --> 22:25.011
I can't believe that I,
a dignified Duke,

22:25.141 --> 22:27.530
was deceived by this rebellious child.

22:27.531 --> 22:29.400
I personally handed over a golden goose

22:29.401 --> 22:32.940
to this brat's hand, which allows him
to train his private army,

22:32.941 --> 22:34.180
win people's hearts,

22:34.181 --> 22:35.290
and have the money

22:35.291 --> 22:36.370
to support his spies

22:36.371 --> 22:38.301
when he had none earlier!

22:40.361 --> 22:41.960
I've practically prepared my neck

22:41.961 --> 22:44.021
for this brat to chop off!

22:44.161 --> 22:47.381
Is there anyone more foolish
than me in this world?

22:47.481 --> 22:48.741
No.

22:49.641 --> 22:51.301
Your Grace! Your Grace!

22:52.361 --> 22:55.080
Someone! Help!

22:55.081 --> 22:57.461
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

23:10.481 --> 23:13.021
What's wrong? Can't stand up straight?

23:13.841 --> 23:15.861
Feeling wronged?

23:17.601 --> 23:19.381
As the lady of the house,

23:20.761 --> 23:22.741
you need to act like one.

23:22.841 --> 23:25.200
You can't just do

23:25.201 --> 23:27.581
whatever you want.

23:29.861 --> 23:30.960
Forgive me, Sister-in-law.

23:30.961 --> 23:32.341
I was careless for a moment...

23:32.521 --> 23:34.501
I think you've been spoiled by Peijin!

23:34.961 --> 23:36.680
You can't even keep him in line.

23:36.681 --> 23:39.800
You promised an appointment,
but it turned into a complete mess.

23:39.801 --> 23:42.000
Now you can't even handle
a pair of chopsticks.

23:42.001 --> 23:43.861
What can you even do?

23:44.201 --> 23:45.701
You are right.

23:54.801 --> 23:57.981
I heard from my daughter
that you've fallen ill.

23:58.361 --> 24:00.941
So I came to visit.

24:02.291 --> 24:04.980
How are you feeling?

24:04.981 --> 24:06.721
It's just a minor illness.

24:07.201 --> 24:09.891
I dare not trouble you.

24:12.961 --> 24:14.080
(I've been courteous)

24:14.081 --> 24:15.581
(and respectful.)

24:15.801 --> 24:18.421
(Why is he still scowling?)

24:19.321 --> 24:21.880
(Was he involved in the plan)

24:21.881 --> 24:24.141
(to have Dou Zhao marry
into the Song Family?)

24:24.641 --> 24:26.421
(How much does he know?)

24:26.681 --> 24:28.240
(Could he be the mastermind)

24:28.241 --> 24:30.941
(behind the whole affair?)

24:32.881 --> 24:34.901
No matter how upset Your Grace gets,

24:35.001 --> 24:37.681
His Lordship always speaks kindly.

24:37.821 --> 24:40.941
True filial piety isn't just
about obedience.

24:40.951 --> 24:43.621
But also respect and demeanor.

24:44.501 --> 24:46.901
That's rare, truly rare.

24:48.761 --> 24:49.901
Your Grace.

24:50.761 --> 24:51.901
Let me do it.

24:55.681 --> 24:56.680
Your Grace,

24:56.681 --> 24:58.941
you must take good care of your health.

25:05.481 --> 25:10.141
Do you and my unfilial son
get along well?

25:11.121 --> 25:12.341
Naturally.

25:13.401 --> 25:15.181
With Yantang being so capable,

25:15.401 --> 25:17.981
you should take it easy

25:18.001 --> 25:19.461
and enjoy life.

25:19.521 --> 25:22.941
Let Yantang handle things.

25:23.921 --> 25:27.461
(Is he implying
I should give up my Duke title?)

25:29.041 --> 25:30.280
As for Ms. Longevity,

25:30.281 --> 25:31.880
I know my daughter well.

25:31.881 --> 25:33.981
She is a well-behaved
and sensible child.

25:34.361 --> 25:37.221
She has been preparing medicine

25:37.241 --> 25:39.781
for you in the kitchen
these past few days.

25:46.081 --> 25:47.040
I am fine.

25:47.041 --> 25:48.181
It's all right.

25:49.201 --> 25:50.341
This...

25:50.361 --> 25:51.501
Your Grace,

25:51.521 --> 25:52.821
take good care of yourself.

25:53.201 --> 25:55.301
You must take the medicine on time

25:55.401 --> 25:57.021
to get better.

25:57.841 --> 26:00.861
I'll go and check on my daughter.

26:06.161 --> 26:07.301
Lyu Zheng.

26:07.641 --> 26:09.981
Lyu Zheng, where are you?

26:12.601 --> 26:13.440
Your Grace,

26:13.441 --> 26:14.661
I'm here.

26:14.841 --> 26:18.080
Has Dou Zhao been preparing
my medicine all this time?

26:18.081 --> 26:20.320
Yes, she knows medicine.

26:20.321 --> 26:22.701
She has been personally preparing it.

26:23.761 --> 26:25.421
You fool!

26:25.441 --> 26:27.661
How could you let her do that?

26:27.761 --> 26:29.941
Are you trying to get me killed sooner?

26:30.161 --> 26:31.501
Remember this.

26:31.521 --> 26:32.901
From now on,

26:33.041 --> 26:35.061
prepare my medicine yourself.

26:35.081 --> 26:36.221
Yes, Your Grace.

26:36.721 --> 26:37.861
Come back here!

26:39.441 --> 26:40.981
Throw away all the herbs

26:41.201 --> 26:42.621
we have now

26:42.921 --> 26:44.800
and buy new ones.

26:44.801 --> 26:45.941
Yes, Your Grace.

27:04.841 --> 27:05.981
Gentler.

27:15.241 --> 27:17.141
The "Lessons for Women" teaches

27:17.281 --> 27:20.541
humility, respect, proper conduct,
and self-discipline.

27:21.921 --> 27:23.101
Madam Jin,

27:24.321 --> 27:26.181
keep an eye on her for me.

27:26.321 --> 27:28.021
If she dares to slack off,

27:28.321 --> 27:29.880
you can punish her on my behalf.

27:29.881 --> 27:31.021
Yes, Your Grace.

27:37.561 --> 27:39.261
Stand up straight against the wall.

27:39.321 --> 27:40.440
Heads up.

27:40.441 --> 27:41.581
Tuck in your stomach.

27:42.161 --> 27:43.821
Straighten your legs.

27:45.681 --> 27:47.301
"Lessons for Women" emphasizes

27:47.481 --> 27:51.101
humility, respect, proper conduct,
and self-discipline.

28:08.521 --> 28:10.101
Open your eyes.

28:11.841 --> 28:13.381
I said, lean against the wall.

28:14.041 --> 28:16.981
Don't even think about slacking off.

28:18.361 --> 28:21.701
I've got this ruler ready for you.

28:28.641 --> 28:30.000
Madam! Madam!

28:30.001 --> 28:31.381
What is it?

28:34.601 --> 28:35.741
She's...

28:37.241 --> 28:38.781
Madam, look!

28:47.721 --> 28:49.200
If I had known she was pregnant,

28:49.201 --> 28:50.960
I wouldn't have punished her.

28:50.961 --> 28:52.821
How do I explain this now?

28:53.001 --> 28:55.240
This is Tingyu's first child.

28:55.241 --> 28:56.120
Madam,

28:56.121 --> 28:57.880
how is this your fault?

28:57.881 --> 28:59.920
Dou Ming has
her wet nurse attending to her.

28:59.921 --> 29:02.040
Is Madam Zhou here only for a display?

29:02.041 --> 29:05.381
Whether she's pregnant or not,
they should have known better.

29:07.801 --> 29:08.920
You're right.

29:08.921 --> 29:11.280
I've always had the family's
best interests at heart.

29:11.281 --> 29:12.880
I'm not at fault.

29:12.881 --> 29:14.190
But Dou Ming knew

29:14.191 --> 29:16.381
she was pregnant

29:16.401 --> 29:18.120
and didn't say a word about it.

29:18.121 --> 29:20.021
Now, she's had a miscarriage.

29:20.041 --> 29:22.141
This is the Wei Family's
flesh and blood.

29:23.321 --> 29:24.901
It's infuriating.

29:25.041 --> 29:26.160
Madam,

29:26.161 --> 29:27.720
you have a kind heart.

29:27.721 --> 29:29.560
But we can't let the Dou Family

29:29.561 --> 29:30.560
throw this blame

29:30.561 --> 29:32.760
onto our family.

29:32.761 --> 29:35.960
Remember, it was your kind heart

29:35.961 --> 29:37.160
that allowed Fifth Young Lady

29:37.161 --> 29:39.901
to marry the Duke
in place of Fourth Young Lady.

29:40.441 --> 29:42.941
As the Duchess of Jing,

29:43.571 --> 29:46.141
I can't make the same mistake twice.

29:46.801 --> 29:48.050
Write them a visiting card.

29:48.051 --> 29:49.461
I need to go to the Dou's Residence

29:50.391 --> 29:51.821
to demand an explanation.

29:52.841 --> 29:53.760
Madam,

29:53.761 --> 29:56.220
I failed to look after the young lady,

29:56.221 --> 29:58.000
causing the tragic loss

29:58.001 --> 30:00.141
of her unborn son.

30:01.831 --> 30:03.341
This isn't your fault.

30:04.841 --> 30:06.941
It's that greedy Wei Tingzhen's fault.

30:07.721 --> 30:09.301
This is all her doing.

30:09.921 --> 30:13.381
Now, the gap in the loan
can't be filled.

30:14.601 --> 30:16.581
She's desperate

30:16.591 --> 30:18.661
because she can't get
the dividends promised to her.

30:19.001 --> 30:20.981
If it weren't
for Dou Zhao telling Master,

30:21.041 --> 30:22.381
how could it not be filled?

30:24.361 --> 30:25.501
This won't do.

30:27.681 --> 30:29.661
We need to think of a solution.

30:30.121 --> 30:32.061
Otherwise, Ming's days

30:32.161 --> 30:33.461
will be even harder.

30:34.281 --> 30:35.280
If it wasn't

30:35.281 --> 30:37.541
for Ming's happiness,

30:38.441 --> 30:40.581
I wouldn't have taken
such desperate measures.

30:41.121 --> 30:44.581
Now, if we can't fill this gap,

30:45.961 --> 30:47.461
not only will that greedy woman,

30:48.161 --> 30:49.541
but even the Cangbei Gang

30:49.921 --> 30:51.701
won't spare us.

30:54.601 --> 30:57.080
Did your grandmother send

30:57.081 --> 30:58.941
these flowers and plants from the manor?

31:00.601 --> 31:02.261
She specifically instructed me

31:02.681 --> 31:04.821
to take good care of them

31:04.881 --> 31:07.021
so they can take root, grow,

31:07.041 --> 31:09.421
and blossom in the capital.

31:09.601 --> 31:10.941
Mother is so thoughtful.

31:11.561 --> 31:14.901
I heard His Lordship personally helped
you transplant them.

31:16.081 --> 31:17.920
Seeing you two support
each other like this

31:17.921 --> 31:20.101
puts me at ease.

31:26.321 --> 31:27.461
Father,

31:28.041 --> 31:29.901
did something happen?

31:33.081 --> 31:34.621
The family just reported

31:35.841 --> 31:36.981
that Ming

31:38.081 --> 31:39.080
had a miscarriage.

31:39.081 --> 31:40.221
What?

31:44.441 --> 31:46.821
You taught your daughter well!

31:47.321 --> 31:49.341
Not only does she defy
her sister-in-law,

31:49.521 --> 31:51.341
but she also hides her pregnancy

31:51.961 --> 31:54.221
and harms the Wei Family's heir.

31:56.121 --> 31:58.261
Take Ming back with you.

31:59.241 --> 32:01.021
Our household is too small

32:01.401 --> 32:03.661
to accommodate such a difficult person.

32:03.841 --> 32:05.021
The nerve of you.

32:06.001 --> 32:07.941
I haven't even asked you
for an explanation.

32:08.801 --> 32:10.501
Yet, you're turning the tables

32:10.641 --> 32:12.461
to accuse me first.

32:13.081 --> 32:15.781
It was Wei Tingyu
who agreed to this marriage.

32:16.161 --> 32:17.781
If he wants to break the engagement now,

32:18.191 --> 32:20.901
he should be the one to speak up.

32:21.181 --> 32:23.821
I've just arranged
a respectable post for him,

32:24.201 --> 32:26.000
and now you want
to turn your back on us?

32:26.001 --> 32:29.941
My brother dismissed all his concubines
for your daughter.

32:30.121 --> 32:31.981
Who else in the Capital can do that?

32:32.601 --> 32:34.581
I know exactly

32:34.831 --> 32:36.511
what you're plotting.

32:36.601 --> 32:38.101
Ming's child was lost

32:38.441 --> 32:41.021
because of you.

32:41.041 --> 32:43.301
If you can't give me
an explanation today,

32:43.761 --> 32:45.800
we'll take this to the Shengtian Court.

32:45.801 --> 32:47.021
Sure!

32:47.241 --> 32:50.240
The Governor of Shengtian
can settle this too.

32:50.241 --> 32:52.640
The agreement was
for the Fourth Young Lady to marry.

32:52.641 --> 32:54.661
But the bride on that day
was Fifth Young Lady.

32:54.801 --> 32:57.280
If you hadn't swapped the bride,

32:57.281 --> 32:59.341
would this miscarriage have happened?

32:59.441 --> 33:01.140
If Dou Zhao had married into our family,

33:01.141 --> 33:03.280
there would be no trouble,

33:03.281 --> 33:04.741
no jealousy, and no resentment.

33:05.411 --> 33:08.141
Madam Wang, do you still remember

33:08.561 --> 33:10.661
what you owe me?

33:13.961 --> 33:16.120
Madam, the bride swap is one thing,

33:16.121 --> 33:17.200
but the loan shark issue

33:17.201 --> 33:19.301
cannot be taken to the authorities.

33:19.921 --> 33:21.080
Dou Ming

33:21.081 --> 33:23.781
has no demeanor as the head lady.

33:23.921 --> 33:25.421
She defied her elders

33:25.561 --> 33:28.200
and used the child to spite us.

33:28.201 --> 33:30.261
With such a vicious heart,

33:30.281 --> 33:32.200
even if we go to Shengtian Court,

33:32.201 --> 33:34.560
- it will end up in a divorce!
- You!

33:34.561 --> 33:37.341
Duchess of Jing,
your words are truly strange.

33:41.041 --> 33:43.421
Why would Ming harm her own child?

33:49.041 --> 33:50.661
As a woman,

33:50.761 --> 33:53.920
don't you know that a miscarriage
is like a serious illness?

33:53.921 --> 33:56.621
And one carelessness can be fatal?

33:56.681 --> 33:58.621
Ming just married Duke of Jining,

33:58.711 --> 34:00.181
and they are still in love.

34:00.441 --> 34:02.261
Why would she risk her life?

34:05.001 --> 34:07.381
Even a tiger doesn't eat its own cubs.

34:07.561 --> 34:10.320
If it weren't
for the Duchess' punishments,

34:10.321 --> 34:12.741
Her Ladyship wouldn't
have had a miscarriage.

34:12.961 --> 34:14.301
You insolent servant!

34:14.641 --> 34:16.461
Who gave you the right to speak?

34:16.731 --> 34:19.161
So the Duke of Jining's household
has such strict rules.

34:19.441 --> 34:20.981
To torment the daughter-in-law,

34:21.141 --> 34:22.951
you don't even care
about the family's heir?

34:22.961 --> 34:24.101
That's...

34:24.121 --> 34:26.221
That's just nonsense.

34:26.481 --> 34:29.741
Our family already has few descendants.

34:30.401 --> 34:32.821
Dou Ming was having Tingyu's child.

34:32.841 --> 34:35.901
Why wouldn't my brother
and I don't want the child?

34:36.561 --> 34:37.701
The child is lost,

34:38.121 --> 34:40.280
and everyone thinks it's Ming's fault.

34:40.281 --> 34:42.501
Duchess of Jing,
you're aggressively assertive.

34:42.641 --> 34:43.781
Those who know might think

34:43.961 --> 34:46.061
you're concerned about the lineage.

34:46.301 --> 34:47.541
But those who don't might think

34:47.721 --> 34:50.381
you're taking the chance
to humiliate your sister-in-law.

34:50.391 --> 34:51.911
- Dou Ming had a miscarriage.
- No, it's not like that.

34:51.921 --> 34:53.781
The Dou Family haven't said anything.

34:54.401 --> 34:55.840
Yet you keep insisting on going

34:55.841 --> 34:57.461
to the Shengtian Court.

34:57.481 --> 35:00.760
Conveniently, Governor Dai is an old
acquaintance of my Fifth Uncle.

35:00.761 --> 35:02.221
Let's go ask for his judgment.

35:04.111 --> 35:05.680
- I... No...
- Su Lan.

35:05.681 --> 35:06.520
Yes, Young Lady.

35:06.521 --> 35:07.661
Send someone

35:07.801 --> 35:09.181
to the Shengtian Court.

35:09.441 --> 35:10.581
Yes.

35:11.321 --> 35:12.461
No...

35:14.521 --> 35:15.661
Madam!

35:15.761 --> 35:16.640
Madam!

35:16.641 --> 35:18.741
Why aren't you sending a physician?

35:20.081 --> 35:22.421
Since the Duchess is unwell,

35:22.641 --> 35:25.181
she should rest in the warm room
next door.

35:26.001 --> 35:28.461
We will discuss this another day.

35:29.281 --> 35:30.781
Madam...

35:45.041 --> 35:46.981
Swapping the best for the worst.

35:47.841 --> 35:49.341
Unbelievable!

35:55.561 --> 35:57.821
Ming was determined
to marry into this family.

35:58.521 --> 36:00.421
And I already knew this would happen.

36:00.881 --> 36:02.541
Ming has been obedient since childhood

36:03.081 --> 36:04.841
and insists on marrying
as your replacement.

36:05.201 --> 36:07.581
She endured her sister-in-law's torment

36:07.721 --> 36:09.341
and now suffered a miscarriage.

36:10.201 --> 36:11.821
All of this

36:12.121 --> 36:14.160
is because of you.

36:14.161 --> 36:16.381
I came here for two reasons.
First, for the Dou Family,

36:16.801 --> 36:18.621
and second, to avoid making Father sad.

36:19.841 --> 36:22.181
If you repay kindness with ingratitude,

36:22.441 --> 36:24.101
then it's my own fault for interfering.

36:25.761 --> 36:27.781
What a hypocrite.

36:30.561 --> 36:31.701
Let's go

36:32.601 --> 36:34.221
and bring Ming home.

37:01.721 --> 37:02.941
Why are you here?

37:03.161 --> 37:05.501
I've been following you
since you arrived here.

37:05.601 --> 37:07.181
At first, I was worried.

37:07.241 --> 37:10.541
But seeing you handle the situation
with such eloquence and ease,

37:11.001 --> 37:12.221
I am now at ease.

37:13.081 --> 37:14.680
Would I suffer grievances

37:14.681 --> 37:16.141
in my own home?

37:16.321 --> 37:17.320
No.

37:17.321 --> 37:20.061
I just love seeing
my wife handle matters so skillfully.

37:24.041 --> 37:25.181
Don't worry.

37:25.441 --> 37:28.040
These are just disputes
among the women in the household.

37:28.041 --> 37:29.541
I can handle it.

37:29.801 --> 37:32.061
This is Wei Tingyu's problem.

37:32.521 --> 37:34.021
I've already sent someone to find him.

37:36.761 --> 37:37.901
Yantang,

37:38.681 --> 37:40.381
I want to see Dou Ming.

37:46.041 --> 37:48.381
Madam, you should drink a little.

37:48.561 --> 37:50.301
Your health is most important.

37:50.321 --> 37:51.320
I'll feed her.

37:51.321 --> 37:52.461
Madam.

37:59.081 --> 38:00.221
Here.

38:01.981 --> 38:03.121
What's the matter?

38:03.621 --> 38:06.061
I just faced
your sister-in-law's temper at home,

38:06.221 --> 38:08.221
and now I have to see yours.

38:09.521 --> 38:11.421
I know what you want to say.

38:12.281 --> 38:14.101
No need to say more.

38:15.561 --> 38:18.061
A miscarriage is like a serious illness.

38:18.281 --> 38:19.781
A simple bowl of sweet water

38:19.921 --> 38:21.581
cannot restore her health.

38:21.921 --> 38:23.541
It might leave side effects.

38:25.011 --> 38:26.151
Ming,

38:26.461 --> 38:28.061
why not come back with me?

38:28.381 --> 38:29.981
I'll help you recover well.

38:34.921 --> 38:36.581
You're the only one

38:37.281 --> 38:39.501
who treats this impoverished household
like treasure.

38:41.121 --> 38:42.200
Ming,

38:42.201 --> 38:43.701
no need to worry.

38:44.361 --> 38:46.261
I will take care of everything.

38:46.441 --> 38:47.781
The most important thing

38:48.081 --> 38:50.621
is to recuperate well, understand?

38:52.121 --> 38:53.261
Mother.

38:55.321 --> 38:56.461
Mother.

39:03.961 --> 39:05.501
Take this money.

39:05.561 --> 39:07.101
Buy some tonics for Ming

39:07.121 --> 39:08.480
and keep the rest for yourself.

39:08.481 --> 39:09.480
Remember,

39:09.481 --> 39:11.221
don't give all of it to Ming,

39:11.371 --> 39:13.261
or that greedy woman will take it away.

39:13.961 --> 39:15.000
Yes, Madam.

39:15.001 --> 39:15.920
But Madam,

39:15.921 --> 39:18.280
this money is
for filling the gap in the loan.

39:18.281 --> 39:20.741
If the Cangbei Gang
doesn't get their money...

39:21.201 --> 39:22.081
She's right.

39:22.091 --> 39:24.511
I'm worried that the untrustworthy ones
might come looking for us.

39:24.521 --> 39:25.800
If we can't get rid of them,

39:25.801 --> 39:27.141
it will be a big problem.

39:27.281 --> 39:28.480
Use it for Ming first.

39:28.481 --> 39:30.181
I'll figure out the rest.

39:30.281 --> 39:33.221
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

39:37.481 --> 39:38.400
Zhao...

39:38.401 --> 39:39.541
Ming.

39:46.721 --> 39:48.821
Wei Tingyu is truly unreliable.

39:49.121 --> 39:50.661
How could he let this happen to you?

39:51.281 --> 39:53.840
If he hadn't let his sister control
the household affairs,

39:53.841 --> 39:55.501
this wouldn't have happened.

39:56.481 --> 39:58.061
I don't blame him.

39:59.161 --> 40:01.861
His Lordship has always preferred
the vast outdoors.

40:02.041 --> 40:03.541
Being confined in this house

40:03.921 --> 40:05.821
always makes him unhappy.

40:08.041 --> 40:09.941
You've told me

40:10.521 --> 40:12.981
that His Lordship wasn't a good husband,

40:13.761 --> 40:17.301
and the Duke of Jining's Residence
isn't a good place to settle.

40:17.881 --> 40:20.261
But I always thought

40:20.901 --> 40:22.581
that no matter
how difficult things were,

40:23.401 --> 40:25.261
as long as the two of us were united,

40:25.761 --> 40:29.341
we could live a good life
behind closed doors.

40:31.001 --> 40:32.221
Do you regret it?

40:36.561 --> 40:38.061
Divorce him, Ming.

40:39.361 --> 40:42.101
This is your best chance to escape.

40:43.201 --> 40:44.341
Zhao.

40:45.481 --> 40:47.760
If you and Lord Song

40:47.761 --> 40:49.581
ever find yourselves
in a similar situation,

40:50.761 --> 40:52.741
what would you choose?

41:01.241 --> 41:02.910
Lu Ming exhausted three horses

41:02.911 --> 41:04.541
to find this scoundrel in Jiaozhou.

41:05.281 --> 41:06.421
Ming,

41:07.131 --> 41:08.271
it's all my fault.

41:09.001 --> 41:10.560
If I hadn't acted on my own,

41:10.561 --> 41:12.021
you wouldn't have been punished,

41:12.241 --> 41:14.021
and our child wouldn't be lost.

41:16.881 --> 41:18.061
Wei Tingyu.

41:26.761 --> 41:27.901
Ming,

41:27.921 --> 41:29.061
I am sorry.

41:29.641 --> 41:31.021
I'll take up my post tomorrow.

41:31.121 --> 41:32.541
You can punish me however you want.

41:32.561 --> 41:33.901
Just don't be angry

41:34.081 --> 41:35.581
and harm your health.

41:37.681 --> 41:38.531
Ming,

41:38.541 --> 41:39.960
(Divorce Agreement)
it's my fault.

41:39.961 --> 41:41.221
I'm not a good person.

41:41.231 --> 41:43.280
♪To kiss your brow♪

41:43.281 --> 41:45.941
It's my fault. I'm a disgrace.

41:46.161 --> 41:47.480
I know my mistake, Ming.

41:47.481 --> 41:48.621
Please forgive me.

41:49.081 --> 41:50.760
Forgive me, Ming.

41:50.761 --> 41:51.901
I've made a mistake.

41:52.681 --> 41:54.261
I'm a scum.

41:54.441 --> 41:55.581
Ming.

41:56.081 --> 41:58.120
I'm sorry, Ming.

41:58.121 --> 42:00.981
(Divorce Agreement)

42:01.641 --> 42:03.061
I've wronged you.

42:04.201 --> 42:05.861
I've failed the child.

42:06.441 --> 42:08.421
I've failed our child.

42:09.201 --> 42:10.941
I let you down.

42:13.201 --> 42:15.760
Sir, Madam asked me
to bring you a cloak.

42:15.761 --> 42:17.581
Please take care of your health.

42:20.761 --> 42:21.901
Ming.

42:23.001 --> 42:24.141
Ming.

42:24.641 --> 42:25.781
Are you all right?

42:26.121 --> 42:27.261
I've failed you

42:27.481 --> 42:28.560
and our child.

42:28.561 --> 42:33.731
♪I devote my life and world
to your wishes♪

42:35.401 --> 42:36.541
I don't want to divorce.

42:36.681 --> 42:38.421
Ming, I'm sorry.

42:38.481 --> 42:39.621
I don't want to divorce.

42:39.641 --> 42:41.101
It's my fault. Just hit me.

42:41.401 --> 42:42.280
Hit me.

42:42.281 --> 42:43.240
- Peijin...
- It's my fault.

42:43.241 --> 42:44.381
Peijin.

42:45.041 --> 42:46.741
Every time you hit yourself,

42:47.281 --> 42:49.181
it hurts me too.

42:50.721 --> 42:52.240
I knew you cared about me

42:52.241 --> 42:53.541
and worried about me.

42:53.601 --> 42:54.741
That's all that matters.

42:55.521 --> 42:56.661
But

42:58.801 --> 43:01.060
I can't stay in this house
for another moment.

43:01.061 --> 43:05.240
♪For you, I rise again in this life♪

43:05.241 --> 43:06.381
No.

43:06.481 --> 43:07.981
It's not that you can't stay,

43:08.281 --> 43:11.821
it's that some people must be cut off
from the Duke of Jining's household.

43:14.761 --> 43:15.901
Ming,

43:16.281 --> 43:17.461
wait for me.

43:21.881 --> 43:24.061
Peijin... Peijin!

43:44.361 --> 43:47.661
Is this taking advantage of her
while she's drunk?

43:49.161 --> 43:50.301
Yantang.

43:50.561 --> 43:53.920
Actually, I'm not drunk.

43:53.921 --> 43:57.000
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart♪

43:57.001 --> 43:59.990
♪The dizziness of longing♪

43:59.991 --> 44:03.710
♪Like the sun waiting
for the flying wild geese♪

44:03.711 --> 44:07.101
♪The sound of weapons chasing
the long whip♪

44:07.591 --> 44:13.671
♪Never tired after a hundred battles,
because of you♪

44:13.981 --> 44:15.890
♪Morning and night, we meet again♪

44:15.891 --> 44:17.450
♪Walking slowly towards the distance♪

44:17.451 --> 44:20.821
♪Like leaves tangled in the wind,
tightly intertwined♪

44:20.861 --> 44:22.960
♪Together with you, wing to wing♪

44:22.961 --> 44:27.690
♪Our shadows flying,
dwelling together year after year♪

44:27.691 --> 44:29.470
♪Morning and night, with clear skies♪

44:29.471 --> 44:31.651
♪Clear wind and bright moon,
we wait for them♪

44:31.851 --> 44:34.470
♪Waiting for the fog to disperse
and the clouds to clear♪

44:34.471 --> 44:36.310
♪Tears that fall,
half a lifetime of tears♪

44:36.311 --> 44:40.711
♪Melted by your kiss,
melted by your kiss♪

44:41.251 --> 44:43.440
♪In this life, I wish
to be like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

44:43.441 --> 44:45.411
♪The green shore is more beautiful
than the sky♪

44:45.591 --> 44:48.240
♪The splendor doesn't intoxicate
the eyes♪

44:48.241 --> 44:49.970
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

44:49.971 --> 44:54.990
♪The mountains are distant, what do I have to envy?♪
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

44:54.991 --> 44:57.200
♪In this life,
I wish to keep my promise to you♪

44:57.201 --> 44:59.380
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

44:59.381 --> 45:01.990
♪I will definitely fulfill the promise
without fail♪

45:01.991 --> 45:08.081
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

45:16.351 --> 45:18.500
♪In this life, I wish
to be like Mandarin ducks in the water♪

45:18.501 --> 45:20.631
♪The green shore is more beautiful
than the sky♪

45:20.661 --> 45:23.280
♪The splendor doesn't intoxicate
the eyes♪

45:23.281 --> 45:24.970
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

45:24.971 --> 45:30.020
♪The mountains are distant, what do I have to envy?♪
♪Even so, I don' envy them♪

45:30.021 --> 45:32.100
♪In this life, I wish
to keep my promise to you♪

45:32.101 --> 45:34.311
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

45:34.341 --> 45:36.990
♪I will definitely fulfill the promise
without fail♪

45:36.991 --> 45:43.231
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

45:47.161 --> 45:48.220
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:48.221 --> 45:49.200
